When to Deploy Agent and Gateway
Manage servers only	Agent is required on each managed server.
There are three options to configure Agents to connect the OpsRamp Cloud. See options above.
Manage network and storage devices	Gateways are required to manage network and storage devices.
Each Gateway must connect directly to the OpsRamp Cloud. See options above.
See Gateway sizing guidelines.
Manage servers, network and storage devices	Agent and Gateway are both required.
There are three options to configure Agents and Gateways to connect to the OpsRamp Cloud. See options above.
See Gateway sizing guidelines.
